Do not forget to customise the default values inside the
%%PREFIX%%/libexec/greyscanner script

to enable greyscanner place the following line in rc.conf

 greyscanner_enable="YES"

to collect stats (for example via RRD) you can use the 
spamd_rrd script in %%EXAMPLESDIR%% 
as starting point

